HEADWORD: whatchamacallit
<hw>whatchamacallit</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Any object
whose name is forgotten, or not known.</def> <altsp>[Also spelled
<asp>whachamacallit</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> thingumbob, doohickey, dingus, whatsis,
what-do-you-call-it.</syn>
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

